      p 
        | KPCC is proud to support Live Talks Los Angeles -- presenting compelling, timely and insightful conversations at various venues around the Los Angeles metro area. The evening series features arts and cultural events and the morning series, Live Talks Business Forum, features executives and business thought leaders at the new Gensler headquarters in Downtown Los Angeles.
